LANGUAGE COMMUNITY RIGHTS
The Lingít, Haida, and Tsimshian peoples and their communities may use,
modify, distribute, and commercialize this software and any language data
contributed by their communities without restriction. Language data
contributed by a community belongs to that community. This software does
not and cannot claim ownership of any language, word, grammar, or
cultural knowledge.

